                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850511-40-off226 t17850511-40-cd227"></join> last, one cloth jacket, value 12 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17850511-40-victim470" type="victimName">
